   Tailwind v4 directives (@import "tailwindcss"; then
  @import "./variables.css";).
  3. Create tailwind.config.js: Extend theme to reference CSS
   variables as Tailwind tokens (e.g., colors: { primary: 
  'var(--accent-blue)' }), set content paths for purging.
  4. Create postcss.config.js: Configure Tailwind +
  Autoprefixer processing.
  5. Create styles/components/graph.css: Extract
  graph-specific styles (tooltip, controls, cytoscape
  container) from index.html, using CSS variables for colors.
  6. Update index.html: Remove inline <style> block, import
  only main.css (which cascades to variables + Tailwind +
  component styles).

